description:
A set of 10 emblems and 10 skins awarded as a bonus for purchasing the ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Experimental Aircraft Series Set.

10 Bonus Emblems:
- 4 Nugget emblems commemorating the 25th anniversary of the ACE COMBAT series
- 6 emblems from other games in the series, including Albireo and Beast

10 Bonus Skins:
- 10 skins from enemy squadrons in the series, including CFA-44 Butterfly Master Skin and Su-37 Ofnir Skin.
name: ACE COMBAT™7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Experimental Aircraft Series Special Bonus Set
